--- Axis ---

Axis smiles, "Sure you'll get to kick ass, just not right now. You 
can use the training center after the tour." He nods to 
Hazel, "Right now, I'm going to give you a tour of the base, then 
we'll talk to Aerotaur for orders. Follow me people." He turns the 
corner, and heads into the the control room. "This, my friends, is 
the control room." (ooc: is anyone in here right now? Grounded 
perhaps?) Axis pauses so that the rest of the group can enter the 
room and take a look.
